<\/span>Reasons why you may need to send money abroad.<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Globalization, affordable travelling, and work have made the world look smaller. There are several reasons why you may need money transferred to another country. Some of these reasons include:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>\u2022 Make mortgage payments for homes in foreign countries<br>\u2022 Making payments for services or goods offered from another country<br>\u2022 Sending money to family or friends living in a foreign country<br>\u2022 Setting a business or firm overseas<br>\u2022 Converting the money to spend when travelling abroad<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"what-are-the-best-ways-to-send-money-abroad\"><\/span>What are the best ways to send money abroad?<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>You can transfer money internationally through various channels. The method used depends on multiple factors. Each channel has both advantages and disadvantages. Some of the common ways include:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>\u2022 International transfer service, which involves depositing the money using the local currency and the organization deposits the money into the account of the recipient in the foreign country.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>\u2022 Bank to bank involves placing an order at the financial institution to initiate an international transfer to the receiver\u2019s bank account.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>\u2022 International wire transfers where the remittance services transfer the money directly to the bank account, mobile, or office where the recipient can collect the cash.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>\u2022 Digital banking services involve online banks Digital banks. These institutions are becoming more popular by offering same-day transfers. Digital banks also offer cheaper money transfer options.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>\u2022 Multi-currency debit cards include Visa and Master Cards. One latest invention of the multi-currency debit card is the Verv IBA that combines both digital and physical financial services. These services allow you to use your local card on an international ATM to withdraw currency or make payments.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"the-cheapest-way-to-send-money-abroad\"><\/span>The Cheapest Way to Send Money abroad.<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>People planning to make multiple international money transfers over a long period may opt for financial services that offer low transaction fees. It is best to shop around before selecting the best money transfer channel and avoid high charges. Here are some of the best international money transfer services.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"a-wise-money-transfer\"><\/span>a) Wise money Transfer<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Wise was previously known as TransferWise. It is a popular service provider since with a transparent fee model with no hidden charges. The wise money transfer provider displays the amount of money that the recipient will get. It gives you a summarized report about the fees involved in the financial transaction. Since it is a UK-based company, it complies with UK laws on how to send money abroad.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"b-ofx\"><\/span>b) OFX<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>OFX does not charge any transfer fees. It also offers a competitive exchange rate for currencies above $25000. Most financial services increase their exchange rates when conducting transfers involving large amounts. OFX is the best among the different money transfer organizations. However, it does not offer same-day delivery.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"c-verv-iban-accounts\"><\/span>c) Verv IBAN accounts<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Verv IBAN accounts bridge the physical and digital financial world. You can choose between physical cards and virtual cards when opening a Verv IBAN account. Virtual cards are usable when conducting online transactions.<br>Physical cards allow users to use ATMs and POS. Verv currently operates in more than 120 countries worldwide and has some of the most competitive fees and exchange rates. It offers a transparent international money transfer and also a r<a href=\"http:\/\/localhost:8080\/how-multiple-payment-gateways-help-merchants-sell\/#:~:text=Anyone%20looking%20to%20expand%20their%20business%20to%20a%20global%20scale%20should%20consider%20whether%20their%20current%20payment%20provider%20can%20handle%20such%20a%20shift.\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">eliable payment gateway.<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"800\" height=\"400\" src=\"http:\/\/localhost:8080\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/risks-to-send-money-abroad-1.jpg\" alt=\"send money abroad\" class=\"wp-image-570\" srcset=\"http:\/\/localhost:8080\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/risks-to-send-money-abroad-1.jpg 800w, http:\/\/localhost:8080\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/risks-to-send-money-abroad-1-300x150.jpg 300w, http:\/\/localhost:8080\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/risks-to-send-money-abroad-1-768x384.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"the-risks-involved-when-transferring-money-to-foreign-bank-account\"><\/span>The Risks Involved When Transferring Money to Foreign Bank Account.<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n\n\n\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"hidden-exchange-rates\"><\/span>Hidden Exchange Rates.<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Most financial services lock your exchange rate after providing you with a quote. One of the best actions to take is to transfer the money using the currency of the foreign receiving bank to help avoid excess exchange fees.<br>If unable to do the conversion, ensure that you understand all the underlying costs associated with the financial transaction. Most banks and financial institutions may use low exchange rates to attract customers only to increase them afterward.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"hidden-transaction-fees\"><\/span>Hidden Transaction Fees.<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>When selecting the right financial institution, ensure that you are aware of any costs. Most of these institutions provide potential clients with the mid-market rate that they use with other banks. Some charge transfer fees together with commission fees.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"time-limits-and-delays\"><\/span>Time Limits and Delays.<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Different institutions offer varying services. Some of these services are best for small money transfers, while others are best for bulk transfers. It is important to identify the limits, especially when it involves long-term money transfers.<br>Large and well-established companies also incur delays when making transactions. However, the best financial institutions have well-stipulated compensation policies in case delays occur.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"bottom-line-on-the-best-way-to-transfer-money-internationally\"><\/span>Bottom Line on the Best Way to transfer money internationally.<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Sending money abroad involves several risks making it a challenging task. However, numerous providers offer clients the best way to transfer money internationally without any difficulties. Verv is one of the best channels to choose when transferring money to a foreign bank account. It has both physical and digital debit cards that allow both physical and online money transfers.<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>The financial services industry is changing rapidly. Cheaper and flexible options to send money abroad are coming up.